Chris, you cannot let that stop you from getting a good education.

54
00:02:39,804 --> 00:02:42,310
我们又不是送你去讨人喜欢的 宝贝
We didn't send you over there to be liked, baby.

55
00:02:42,311 --> 00:02:43,278
说的对
Got that right.

56
00:02:43,301 --> 00:02:46,089
妈妈 我在那唯一学到的就是逃跑
Mom, the only thing I'm learning over there is how to get jumped on.

57
00:02:46,128 --> 00:02:48,214
我怎么就不能去桑福德中学呢?
How come I can't go to Lamont Sanford Junior High?

58
00:02:48,250 --> 00:02:50,023
- 就隔几个街区而已 - 不行
- It's only a few blocks away. - Mm-mm, no.

59
00:02:50,058 --> 00:02:52,256
你不能去这附近的学校
You are not going to school in this neighborhood.

60
00:02:52,303 --> 00:02:55,862
你还记得去年有个女孩在玛拉吉中学被人捅了一刀吗?
You remember that girl that got stabbed last year at Marla Gibbs High School?

61
00:02:55,863 --> 00:02:59,484
