Chris, Sanford has nothing but juvenile delinquents and future convicts.

62
00:02:59,711 --> 00:03:03,454
一个人把我出卖给便衣而被判了10年
A man just got ten years because he sold me to an undercover cop.

63
00:03:03,601 --> 00:03:04,424
那么我是?
What am I?

64
00:03:04,535 --> 00:03:07,012
大麻 可卡因 海洛英 还是快克?
Weed, cocaine, heroin or crack?

65
00:03:07,536 --> 00:03:08,787
- Rachel - 是快克
- Rachel. - Crack.

66
00:03:10,143 --> 00:03:11,800
- 但是妈妈 - 但是没用 Chris
- But Mom... - But nothing, Chris.

67
00:03:12,541 --> 00:03:15,152
还有你是怎么弄的满身油漆?
And how did you get paint all over you, anyway?

68
00:03:15,195 --> 00:03:17,098
我去店里玩炸弹人
I went to the store to go play Ms. Pacman.

69
00:03:17,227 --> 00:03:19,199
啊哈! 瞧见没?
Aha! Ah! See there?

70
00:03:19,377 --> 00:03:21,556
要是你一开始就不去那里
See, now, had you not been there in the first place,

71
00:03:21,557 --> 00:03:22,907
你就不会搞的一团糟
you wouldn't be in this mess.

72
00:03:22,908 --> 00:03:25,741
我不断的讲 家和学校两点一线
I keep telling you, come straight home from school.

73
00:03:26,113 --> 00:03:27,779
或许你现在该听我的话了
Maybe now you'll listen to me.

74
00:03:28,017 --> 00:03:30,469
听着 我知道你不喜欢去Corleone
Look, I know you don't like going to Corleone.

75
00:03:30,470 --> 00:03:32,803
但是万事多磨难
But everything is not supposed to be easy.

76
00:03:33,122 --> 00:03:34,122
你明白吗?
You understand me?

77
00:03:36,990 --> 00:03:38,943
上楼去把衣服脱了吧
Now, go upstairs and get out of those clothes.

78
00:03:38,944 --> 00:03:39,944
是的 妈妈
Yes, ma'am.

79
00:03:42,339 --> 00:03:44,435
他咋了 看起来像个湿嗒嗒的小丑
What happened to him? He looks like a wet mime.

80
00:03:44,470 --> 00:03:46,790
没事 他在学校出了点意外
Nothing, he got in an accident at school.

81
00:03:47,161 --> 00:03:50,224
我妈从来不愿意告诉爸爸坏消息
My mother never liked to bother my father with bad news.

82
00:03:50,225 --> 00:03:52,280
像上次Tonya被公车给撞了
Like the time Tonya got hit by a bus.

83
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:54,082
Tonya怎么了?
What happened to Tonya?

84
00:03:54,125 --> 00:03:55,083
没事
Nothing.

85
00:03:56,503 --> 00:03:58,510
还有次Drew的腿给截了
Or the time Drew got his legs cut off.

86
00:03:58,557 --> 00:04:00,327
- Drew怎么了? - 没啥
- What happened to Drew? - Nothing.

87
00:04:04,213 --> 00:04:05,611
你在乐呵个啥?
What are you so happy about?

88
00:04:05,612 --> 00:04:08,113
你记得我去应聘鱼市场的工作吗?
You know that job I applied for down at the fish market?

89
00:04:08,114 --> 00:04:09,453
- 嗯 - 我被聘了!
- Yeah. - I got it!

90
00:04:09,535 --> 00:04:11,027
噢 宝贝 真棒!
Oh, baby, that's great!

91
00:04:11,535 --> 00:04:12,669
恭喜啊
Congratulations.

92
00:04:12,873 --> 00:04:13,873
嗯
Yeah.

93
00:04:14,025 --> 00:04:16,326
比俺两份工资加起来还付的多
It pays more than my other two jobs combined.

94
00:04:16,365 --> 00:04:18,024
真棒! 我要去逛街!
That's great! I get to shop!

95
00:04:20,422 --> 00:04:24,496
这些年头一回我只需要打一份工
Man, for the first time in years I only have to work one job.

96
00:04:25,167 --> 00:04:26,867
而且我只要白天工作
And I'll be working during the day.

97
00:04:26,868 --> 00:04:28,335
感觉像是退休一样
It's going to feel like retirement.

98
00:04:28,336 --> 00:04:30,136
也就是说我们每天放学后
So does this mean we don't have to be quiet

99
00:04:30,137 --> 00:04:31,887
就不用保持安静啦?
every day when we come home from school?

100
00:04:31,888 --> 00:04:34,554
6点前 想怎么大声就怎么大声
You can make all the noise you want, until 6:00.

101
00:04:35,147 --> 00:04:38,424
嘿 爸爸 我们可以开始在超市买些名牌吗?
Hey, Dad, can we start buying name brands at the store now?

102
00:04:39,448 --> 00:04:41,219
- 仅限奥利奥 - 真酷
- Just Oreos. - That's cool.

103
00:04:41,347 --> 00:04:42,513
我们需要庆祝下
We  need to celebrate.

104
00:04:42,607 --> 00:04:44,662
做些我们未曾做过的
Do something we've never done before.

105
00:04:44,863 --> 00:04:46,917
意思是去看场电影后
That can mean anything from going to the movies

106
00:04:46,918 --> 00:04:48,918
接着手拉着手回客厅
to holding hands in the living room.

107
00:04:49,613 --> 00:04:51,592
嗨 爸爸 我们能去玩大逃亡吗?
Hey, Dad. Can we go to Great Escape?

108
00:04:51,627 --> 00:04:52,716
游乐场?
The amusement park?

109
00:04:52,772 --> 00:04:54,311
嗯 能去吗? 拜托啦
Yeah,  can we go? Please?

110
00:04:55,587 --> 00:04:56,587
好吧 宝贝
Sure, baby.

111
00:04:56,787 --> 00:04:57,787
真棒!
Yes!

112
00:04:57,788 --> 00:04:58,899
我去告诉Chris
I got to tell Chris.

113
00:04:59,102 --> 00:05:01,740
既然我妈妈不准我离开Corleone
Since my mother wouldn't let me leave Corleone,

114
00:05:01,827 --> 00:05:03,463
我不得不疯狂的策划下
I had to take drastic measures.

115
00:05:03,758 --> 00:05:05,980
你想让你自己被踢出去?
You're going to get yourself kicked out?

116
00:05:06,207 --> 00:05:07,256
我不得不离开这儿
I have to get out of here.

117
00:05:07,257 --> 00:05:08,812
还有别的选择吗?
What other choice do I have?

118
00:05:09,317 --> 00:05:10,317
不知道
I don't know.

119
00:05:10,516 --> 00:05:12,516
我只是有点舍不得你离开
I guess I just don't want you to go.

120
00:05:12,668 --> 00:05:14,117
你把我一人丢在这儿
You leave me here by myself...

121
00:05:14,118 --> 00:05:15,118
我就完了
I'm toast.

122
00:05:15,281 --> 00:05:16,326
你会没事的
You'll be all right.

123
00:05:16,349 --> 00:05:19,214
他们唯一来找你麻烦的理由 就是因为你跟我在屁股后面
The only reason why they mess with you is 'cause you hang out with me.

124
00:05:19,237 --> 00:05:20,310
你会找交些新朋友啊
You'll find new friends.

125
00:05:20,327 --> 00:05:21,549
但是我们小团队 哥们
But we're a team, man.

126
00:05:21,979 --> 00:05:23,386
我们就像是《警界双雄》里得Starsky和Hutch
We're like Starsky and Hutch.

127
00:05:23,387 --> 00:05:24,387
