Gemini.

137
00:05:39,107 --> 00:05:41,706
好吧 某个小酷猫在海上绕世界航行
All right. This cool cat sailed around the world

138
00:05:41,707 --> 00:05:43,873
同船的还有Pinta和Santa Maria
on the Nia, Pinta and the Santa Maria.

139
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:46,626
如果你能拼出他的名字
I will give you a year's supply of Black Fro Sheen

