Now boy, I asked you a question-- what you looking at?

420
00:18:01,031 --> 00:18:01,994
没啥
Nothing.

421
00:18:02,041 --> 00:18:03,897
你说什么? 我们什么也不是?
So what you trying to say? We're nothing now?

422
00:18:03,898 --> 00:18:04,898
我只是
I just...

423
00:18:05,293 --> 00:18:07,722
我禁不住想起要是Greg也在这儿
