Now I'm back to two jobs.

435
00:18:44,111 --> 00:18:46,444
嗯 现在他的第2份工作是哲学家
Yeah, now his second job is a philosopher.

436
00:18:50,191 --> 00:18:51,589
怎么尝起来像是鱼腥味
That tastes like fish.

